{"tid":545878,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中情局長：各國可以合作做更多，對抗中國間諜活動","createTime":"2018-01-31T03:05:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-13T19:41:32.000Z","uid":147314,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dd2598162663c62ebd39f851f57d370a5d9bd77f","tid":545878,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T03:05:39.000Z","msg":"中情局長指中國間諜活動較俄羅斯對美國影響更大<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1378262_1_L_20180131091733.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1378262_1_L_20180131091733.jpg&h=e9cd3237&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蓬佩奧指中國間諜活動對美國影響較俄國更大。（美聯社資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n美國中央情報局局長蓬佩奧說，中國針對西方國家暗中致力運用影響力，情況與俄羅斯的顛覆活動同樣令人關注，他又認為，中國人的間諜行為，影響範圍比俄國人的更廣。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧接受英國廣播公司訪問時舉例說，中國致力竊取美國的商業情報，並滲透學校和醫院，這些活動更擴展到歐洲和英國。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，各國可以合作做更多，對抗中國試圖在西方施展力量。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1378262-20180131.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1378262-20180131.htm&d=8Bx7RVfFyB9QLKvfWl4srIsQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=256772db\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1378262-20180131.htm&h=6a6ad883\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1378262-20180131.htm</a>"},{"pid":"a74b802c826b1622f953cd3591e2f95d39f446d1","tid":545878,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T03:08:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65641d61e107f73d4def79c2042d2a2ad80e3958","tid":545878,"uid":84212,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T03:13:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"628b2675207bc1d6ef4d785ebef43dec15ddcf5a","tid":545878,"uid":34103,"like